import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col, Card } from 'react-bootstrap'
import TodoListForm from '../todos/TodoListForm'
const Home = () => {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Card>
            <Card.Body>
                <Card.Title>Todo List App</Card.Title>
                <Container>
                    <Row>
                        <Col lg={4} md={4}>
                            <TodoListForm />
                            <ListTable />
                        </Col>
                        <Col lg={8} md={8}>2 of 2</Col>
                    </Row>
                </Container>
            </Card.Body>
            </Card>
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default Home
